{"tid":1920271,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"身家驚人？上原亞衣被騙2千萬超淡定","createTime":"2020-03-11T10:49:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-11T11:40:13.000Z","uid":25345,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0e2dbf387cb9077e2a984fee256d754401807ad6","tid":1920271,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T10:49:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/g4A._NaSOiynWxMSpY8WXg--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTEwO2g9NTEw/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/setn.com.tw/3f9b30a8107b387c97f952763aa993cf\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fg4A._NaSOiynWxMSpY8WXg--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTEwO2g9NTEw%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fko%2Fsetn.com.tw%2F3f9b30a8107b387c97f952763aa993cf&h=a177b639&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/FXqKM8eie5_qKyJc7lVa_w--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTEwO2g9Njgw/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/setn.com.tw/12235c774c3a5f97c3c9ef32c39810d0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FFXqKM8eie5_qKyJc7lVa_w--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTEwO2g9Njgw%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fko%2Fsetn.com.tw%2F12235c774c3a5f97c3c9ef32c39810d0&h=d0679893&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n前AV天后上原亞衣有著甜美外型和火辣身材，是AV界「童顏巨乳」的代名詞，有著超夯人氣的她在2016年宣布引退，隨後更關閉推特帳號，令粉絲們相當不捨，不過上原亞衣今年6月重新開啟個人社群平台與粉絲互動，以藝人身分重新回到大眾視野，日前她參加節目錄影，透露自己踏入及引退AV界的原因，還自爆曾被騙走2000萬元（約新台幣583萬元）。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上原亞衣日前參加電視節目錄影，透露自己是為了賺錢和克服自卑心理而入行，而過去的她其實喜歡浮誇一點的造型，與螢幕上的一頭黑色長直髮、清純形象很不一樣，不過因為清純的模樣比較受到歡迎，因此便轉變路線。<br />\n<br />\n19歲就在AV界出道的上原亞衣也分享了自己當AV女優時期的生活，以「企劃單體女優」活動的她，最忙的時候曾經一個月休息不到5天，甚至在拍攝現場昏倒，也經常生病，時常一邊拍片一邊進出醫院。因為這樣過於忙碌的生活，上原亞衣在全力衝刺幾年、成功站上業界頂點後，自覺存了不少錢的她決定引退，放個大假好好休息、充實自己。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n至於外界相當好奇，作為AV天后的她收入如何？上原亞衣則透露全盛期時，最高月收入能買一輛進口車，雖然實際數字被消音處理，但同是AV女優的高橋聖子聽完後露出驚訝表情，顯見數字相當可觀。不過努力賺錢、存錢的她，卻曾碰上詐欺損失2000萬元，但她對此淡然以對，只說：「就當做人生上了一課吧。」"},{"pid":"78d65e2eee8fe07e474c0f1546e5b592a1ddb27c","tid":1920271,"uid":258649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T10:51:18.000Z","msg":"2000萬日元？"},{"pid":"ee2cf274283a86fdb5b38ef13bdb104aa9503af9","tid":1920271,"uid":2267,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"78d65e2eee8fe07e474c0f1546e5b592a1ddb27c","tid":1920271,"uid":258649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T10:51:18.000Z","msg":"2000萬日元？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T10:55:06.000Z","msg":"英磅呀，議員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28ab35e45a5d55a592e5022557b12cf06af5099d","tid":1920271,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T11:06:26.000Z","msg":"可以射精入佢陰道嗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f28c5a5f60911fda502185d962ab01e2fc673c7b","tid":1920271,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"78d65e2eee8fe07e474c0f1546e5b592a1ddb27c","tid":1920271,"uid":258649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T10:51:18.000Z","msg":"2000萬日元？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T11:07:15.000Z","msg":"Me"},{"pid":"82c99ac5fee350c3d45bc87a3f6d71168dc42d8d","tid":1920271,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T11:17:58.000Z","msg":"應該有幾億"},{"pid":"2e30c45ac5440d5d3b067f1769220e4deec0c9af","tid":1920271,"uid":9594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T11:40:13.000Z","msg":"好女仔 想屌"}]}